The '''Under Secretary of Scout Services''', also referred to as the '''Under Minister of Scout Services''', was the highest-ranking bureaucrat in the [[Bureau of Scouting and Exploration Services|New Republic Scout Service]]. The Under Secretary answered directly to the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic's]] [[Minister of State]], and had oversight of all the divisions of the NRSS.

